      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile,<strong> </strong>deseed the<strong> red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely slice the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced pepper</strong>, <strong>sliced onion</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a baking tray and put it in the oven for 10-15 min until softened and starting to brown</p>",
